The paper focuses on the performance analysis of DSRC communication for intelligent transportation systems, which falls under the category of networked systems (cs.NI). The study also involves analyzing the effect of environmental factors on DSRC performance, which can be related to information theory (cs.IT) and control systems (cs.SY). Additionally, the paper discusses the potential impact of DSRC on safety and mobility, which can be related to cybersecurity (cs.CR) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
